\SE[0]I'm sorry, I've been a little... busy lately.
\SE[0]I'm currently living in Yuriseen now... It's a bit far
away.

\SE[0]The two from earlier... 'Laura' and 'Lunaroa'. They
are my saviors... and my new friends... \SE[0]No, maybe...
my 'new family'...

\SE[2]At first, I was planning to go to that place sooner...
\SE[0]But I decided to try a little harder. \SE[0]It seems
like I'm needed too...

\SE[0]Ah, those two from earlier. They're like a lovey-
dovey couple. Whenever they have a chance, they're all
lovey-dovey with each other. \SE[0]I bet they're still
sneaking kisses behind some corner even now.

\SE\SE[0]'Laura' is... bright and kind. \!\SE[0]Even
when I'm feeling down, I don't show it much on my face, but
Laura can still tell. \!\SE[0]Also, I never get tired of
watching her as a pure-hearted maiden in love.

\SE[25] Lunaroa is... well, she's usually a reliable
person... \SE[4] But every now and then, she becomes like a
runaway train. \SE[1] Did you know? She accidentally made a
big hole in the ground, so we can't go into the cave
anymore. \SE[25] It's kind of funny, isn't it...

\SE[0]She's not here, but there's also a girl named
'Vega'... \!\SE[0]She's like a serious, honor student type.
\!\SE[2]Since everyone here is pretty laid-back, she takes
the initiative and helps organize things...

\SE[0]Every day... is really fun. \!\SE[2]I don't do much
hunting anymore, but instead, I've started doing work for
the guild....

\SE[39]If... \SE[38]Aisha was also here... \SE[60]I often
think it would have been even more fun.

\SE[44]Ah... I can't... tears are about to come out.
\!\SE[61]If I show that side of me... it'll make you
worried, right?

\SE[0]Today... let's stop here, okay? \!\SE[0]Even if I
don't say it, I think you already know... \.No matter how
much time passes... \!\SE[55]I won't forget about Aisha or
anything like that.

\SE[55]It suited Aisha well.... \SE[54]I wanted to see her
wearing this and becoming a grown-up....

\SE[56]Can I borrow this for a moment? \SE[57]Sometimes,
I feel really lonely... \SE[56]I end up crying. \SE[54]But
maybe, if I have this with me, I can cure my crybaby side...

\SE[19]Ah, even if you say no, I'll still borrow it, okay?
\SE[0]This time, it's my turn to have my selfishness
listened to...

\SE[0]Today... let's stop here, okay? \SE[0]See you
later... 'Partner'...

\SE[4]Come here, Sable Noir. \SE[0]Let's go back to
everyone's place.

\SE[14]Surprisingly, are you actually shy around people...?
\!\SE[1]Don't worry! I think everyone is kind. Well, maybe.
It has a collar... It seems like someone's pet dog.
I wonder where this child's master went...
